{"tha-ap260:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap260:0.2":"Thomakavagga ","tha-ap260:0.3":"Pannadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap260:1.1":"“Pabbate himavantamhi, ","tha-ap260:1.2":"vakaciradharo aham; ","tha-ap260:1.3":"Alonapannabhakkhomhi, ","tha-ap260:1.4":"niyamesu ca samvuto. ","tha-ap260:2.1":"Patarase anuppatte, ","tha-ap260:2.2":"siddhattho upagacchi mam; ","tha-ap260:2.3":"Taham buddhassa padasim, ","tha-ap260:2.4":"pasanno sehi panibhi. ","tha-ap260:3.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap260:3.2":"yam pannamadadim tada; ","tha-ap260:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap260:3.4":"pannadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap260:4.1":"Sattavisatikappamhi, ","tha-ap260:4.2":"raja asim sadatthiyo; ","tha-ap260:4.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap260:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap260:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap260:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap260:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap260:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pannadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap260:7.1":"Pannadayakattherassapadanam atthamam. "}